name: The Narrow-Eyed Villain of the Demon Academy
summary: Worst and greatest villain.The narrow-eyed character becomes Asene Adele.Revenge.It was a good sound.At least for the original owner of the body.But from my point of view, the goal is to survive, let alone revenge.I, who did not have the confidence to survive against humans,-I went to the Demon Realm.where I was headed from there.An imperial academy where only the children of prestigious human families gather.  It was a school for demons who terrorize the world.
genres: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Fantasy, Harem, Martial Arts, School Life, Supernatural, Tragedy
